            <h5 class="column-head feature" data-uuid="af74c1c38c4d4d3ab4c6d2e9847cccd4">Slave Populations in the Colonies </h5>
            <p class="intro-feature" data-uuid="4bbc50c138df4858a3dfdb93ede380a3">Because of births and an increase in the slave trade, the slave population in the English colonies grew quickly in the early 1700s.</p>
